OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy across the south overnight with
OL,7,Fpatchy drizzle, especially over hills.
OL,8,FDrier towards the north with some
OL,9,Fclearer spells. A warm night to come,
OL,10,Fespecially in the south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA bright start in the north,
OL,13,Fhowever cloud further south and west
OL,14,Fwill spread northwards throughout the
OL,15,Fday. Patchy rain initially over
OL,16,Fsouthern hills, perhaps a little more
OL,17,Fwidespread later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
