OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,6,Fintervals on Friday, though often
OL,7,Fcloudy with patchy rain in the north
OL,8,Fand west. Fresher on Saturday with
OL,9,Fbright spells then more sunshine on
OL,10,FSunday, and feeling hotter.
